{"tid":1867992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢仔特別鍾意娶豬扒做老婆","createTime":"2020-02-07T11:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T02:36:34.000Z","uid":77320,"like":172,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"28b0652cdaf7383066489a3110710b5269d31934","tid":1867992,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"見到個真&middot;有錢仔（老豆喺大陸有啲唔知乜撚嘢官職）<br />\n25歲就娶老婆<br />\n雖然佢老婆都豬豬地 但係見係真&middot;香港人（黃絲）而且心地幾善良 冇乜嘢啦恭喜佢<br />\n見到個女仔嫁到有錢人都戥佢開心<br />\n<br />\n點知轉個撚頭就離鳩左婚<br />\n個男火速搵到條大陸新女（條女親中嘅 仲好似馬蹄露咁拍片支持中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n今次呢件真係勁撚豬，但係識得打扮嘅<br />\n<br />\n跟住轉過撚頭條女有鳩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱仲訂撚埋婚<br />\n<br />\n越睇佢IG就越覺得成件事痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n離婚搵個新一個好正常<br />\n但咁撚快又結多次婚（梗係條女逼佢中出啦條仔咁撚有錢）就真係癡鳩線<br />\n<br />\n唔使覺得我葡萄<br />\n只係我每次睇到個IG都會擘大個口得個窿<br />\n完全係黑人問號<br />\n<br />\n另外有錢人真係特別鐘意娶豬扒<br />\n因為得豬扒先會係處<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd10545a625e52fca9a7893e883bfe5d3aa26f8","tid":1867992,"uid":213877,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"豬扒有家底。我都想要"},{"pid":"f250443028ae1d44320326a6e953067685f15a2a","tid":1867992,"uid":77320,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"除咗你<br />\n仲有邊個食得落啊屌？"},{"pid":"b529ce8234fc7057400b92088f5a0d692b351ddf","tid":1867992,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"66324af1b5351b885eceec4308b3de14ffa481fd","tid":1867992,"uid":27416,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"你又知人離婚前無同大陸妹一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cca497f04e39b79df0a2fe0113cd31c649da05","tid":1867992,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"cc621d663f82bb642b58cd3d8e29ab77e1e1d202","tid":1867992,"uid":77320,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"66324af1b5351b885eceec4308b3de14ffa481fd","tid":1867992,"uid":27416,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"你又知人離婚前無同大陸妹一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:24:26.000Z","msg":"離婚前定離婚後一齊關我閪事咩<br />\n仲記得同前妻擺酒嗰時 放閃放撚到眼盲<br />\n延開百席咁撚款<br />\n擺撚完酒又離婚<br />\n曬鳩晒啲錢<br />\n仲有佢老竇咁撚廣人面<br />\n都唔知到時點撚樣再請朋友去多次佢個仔個婚禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每兩三年飲一餐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb67ad078984dd1cf9ed845baaaeca489118479","tid":1867992,"uid":77320,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"03cca497f04e39b79df0a2fe0113cd31c649da05","tid":1867992,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:25:07.000Z","msg":"又唔撚係靚擺上黎做乜啫"},{"pid":"8908bcb68da01f1e04f8708ad1c74457a0f6c06d","tid":1867992,"uid":22624,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定係女"},{"pid":"77eab1acad911ac186872a1c322117888db10c36","tid":1867992,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc621d663f82bb642b58cd3d8e29ab77e1e1d202","tid":1867992,"uid":77320,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"66324af1b5351b885eceec4308b3de14ffa481fd","tid":1867992,"uid":27416,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"你又知人離婚前無同大陸妹一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:24:26.000